From: Dipen Patel <dipenp@nvidia.com>
Date: Fri, 26 Apr 2024 01:51:17 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 41/95] NVIDIA: SAUCE: hte: Add tegra264 GTE support

Adding GPIO-GTE mapping and LIC GTE instance support for the tegra264.

http://nvbugs/4401401

Upstream-Status: Backport
Signed-off-by: Dipen Patel <dipenp@nvidia.com>
Signed-off-by: Laxman Dewangan <ldewangan@nvidia.com>
Acked-by: Noah Wager <noah.wager@canonical.com>
Acked-by: Jacob Martin <jacob.martin@canonical.com>
Signed-off-by: Noah Wager <noah.wager@canonical.com>
(cherry picked from commit 766ed1b0b8f76cee4f2d02ff07604d73ed9b1c2c)
Signed-off-by: Matt Madison <matt@madison.systems>
---
 drivers/hte/hte-tegra194.c | 106 +++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
 1 file changed, 106 insertions(+)

diff --git a/drivers/hte/hte-tegra194.c b/drivers/hte/hte-tegra194.c
